SELECT OD.FieldName, ROD.ITDefValue From IT15_RolObjectsD ROD
				INNER JOIN IT15_RolObjectsM ROM ON ROM.RolObjectMID = ROD.RolObjectMID
				INNER JOIN IT15_Roller R ON R.RolID = ROM.RolID
				INNER JOIN IT15_Kullanicilar K ON K.RolID = R.RolID
				INNER JOIN IT15_ObjectsD OD ON OD.ITObjectDID = ROD.ITObjectDID
				WHERE K.KullaniciKodu = dbo.F15_GetKullaniciConn() AND ROM.ITObjectID = 20064 
				AND OD.FieldName IN ('MaliyetType', 'DesenMenseiID', 'KenarTarakEni', 'CozguIscilikDovizBirimID', 'DokumaIscilikDovizBirimID', 'TaharDovizBirimID')
